description: This top 5% Gaston purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 270, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Stringalong for East, Box for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
